ge is that you'll be moving to a new office, and you want to tell all your customers the new location.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid7436902\charrsid7436902 \hich\af2\dbch\af12\loch\f2 Man Student:}{\insrsid7436902\charrsid1115228 \hich\af2\dbch\af12\loch\f2 
